Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&D6D6D6}{\bord2}{\blur0.7\3c&0D0D0D\4c&0D0D0D}便利でしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.55,0:13:43.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&DBD2CC}{\bord2\blur0.7\3c&0D0D0D\4c&0D0D0D}是一级魔法师菲伦小姐对吧
