Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.48,0:16:04.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&D4B696}{\bord1.5\blur0.7\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}最后 连冒险者也很少来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:04.44,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&D4B696}{\bord1.5\blur0.7\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}このとおり　冒険者もめったに訪れぬ土地
