Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.08,0:16:13.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&C9DEF0}{\bord1.7\blur0.7\3c&262626\4c&262626}顺路把它收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:13.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&C9DEF0}{\bord1.7\blur0.7\3c&262626\4c&262626}ついでに討伐しておくよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&C9DAF0\bord2\blur0.7\3c&262626\4c&262626}没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.62,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&C9DAF0\bord2\blur0.7\3c&262626\4c&262626}それでいいよね
