Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:24.86,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\blur2}約束はね　大事にね
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.86,0:01:27.98,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}让它融化在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:27.98,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}温かく残ってる
